# Keep token-bearing tracked files out of `git archive` exports (GH release
# tarballs built by scripts/package_e4_release.sh). `git archive` ignores
# .gitignore, so excluding here is the only way to stop CLAUDE.md (which carries
# live hf_/ghp_/wandb tokens) from shipping inside the asset and self-tripping
# the leak scan. Best long-term fix: stop tracking live tokens in CLAUDE.md.
CLAUDE.md export-ignore

