# all NON-ESSENTIAL to the E.4 code tarball (the actual code src/ configs/
# experiments/ and the node-needed scripts bootstrap_sdc_node.sh / gpu_keeper.py
# / pull_parquets.py are token-CLEAN). Drop the token-bearing non-essential ones
# from the archive so the GH release ships clean. (Tokens still live in the repo
# history → ROTATE + scrub tracked files as the real fix.)
archive/ export-ignore
results/ export-ignore
